  <brief_title>A Research Study to Evaluate Safety and Efficacy of DUR-928 in Subjects With Primary Sclerosing Cholangitis (PSC)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Open-label, Phase 2 Study to Evaluate Safety and Efficacy of DUR-928 in Subjects With Primary Sclerosing Cholangitis (PSC)</official_title>
