  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a research trial testing DUR-928 (an experimental medication). The purpose of the
      trial is to assess whether treatment with DUR-928 has any effect on the treatment of Primary
      Sclerosing Cholangitis (PSC). This trial will also assess safety (side effects).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
